Will Ospreay opens the show with a promo about his disdain for MJF and how he’s got to clean up AEW after MJF messed it up.

MJF fakes an appearance but only addressed Will Ospreay through video on the tron.

MJF challenges Will Ospreay to a match for next week. Ospreay accepts.

